quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  114,1,"Say: \"I seek protection with/by the people`s Lord/master/owner"
  114,2,The people`s king/owner/possessor
  114,3,The people`s God
  114,4,"From bad/evil/harm (of) the inspirer and talker/giver of evil suggestions and temptations (whisperer of evil influences), the devil"
  114,5,Who inspires and talks/gives evil suggestions and temptations in the people`s chests (innermosts)
  114,6,From the Jinns and the people